measurements.description: Twenty-three flowers and 14 buds on five arching to pendulous inflorescences up to 70cm; dorsal sepal hooded, lanceolate, light yellow spotted and blushed burgundy; lateral sepals lanceolate, light yellow, densely spotted burgundy; petals lanceolate, light yellow spotted burgundy, coalescing to blotches centrally; lip light yellow, blotched burgundy; column pale yellow blushed burgundy distally, anther cap cream; substance average; texture matte.
